## Project Structure

```
e2-landing/
├── src/
│   ├── layouts/BaseLayout.astro     ← SEO, fonts, GSAP scroll init
│   ├── styles/global.css            ← Design system (Tailwind v4 @theme tokens)
│   ├── components/
│   │   ├── Hero.astro               ← Gradient hero, badge, CTA
│   │   ├── SocialProof.astro        ← $200M+, 500+, 12x, 48hr stats
│   │   ├── Services.astro           ← 6 flow type cards with hover effects
│   │   ├── CTA.astro                ← Formflow embed placeholder + fallback
│   │   └── Footer.astro             ← Minimal with e2 + Formflow links
│   └── pages/index.astro            ← Composes all sections
├── public/favicon.svg               ← e2 branded
├── PERFORMANCE.md                   ← Speed rules & Lighthouse targets
└── astro.config.mjs                 ← SSG + site URL configured
```

